==Yin Fire Rabbit (丁卯)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦}} year whose final digit is 4 or 9 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)}} or {{ill|Otsu|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)}}), the month of {{ill|February|ja|2月}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)}} of {{ill|Teibou|ja|丁卯}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月}} (from {{ill|Awakening of Insects|ja|啓蟄}} until the day before {{ill|Qingming|ja|清明}}) as applicable.

