==Yin Fire Rabbit (丁卯)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|12=draft|12=draft}} year whose final digit is 4 or 9 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|12=draft|12=draft}} or {{ill|Otsu|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|12=draft|12=draft}}), the month of {{ill|February|ja|2月|12=draft|12=draft}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Teibou|ja|丁卯|12=draft|12=draft}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月|12=draft|12=draft}} (from {{ill|Jingzhe|lt=Awakening of Insects|ja|啓蟄|12=draft|12=draft}} until the day before {{ill|Qingming|ja|清明|12=draft|12=draft}}) as applicable.

