==Yin Fire Rabbit (丁卯)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} year whose final digit is 4 or 9 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|lt=Kinoe (甲)|2=ja|3=甲|4=zh|5=甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=}} or {{ill|Otsu|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|lt=Tsuchinoto (己)|2=ja|3=己|4=zh|5=己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|February|ja|2月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/February|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/February|qq=}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/month (calendar)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/month (calendar)|qq=}} of {{ill|Teibou|ja|1=Yin Fire Rabbit|qq=ja|丁卯|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teibou|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teibou|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Fire Rabbit|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|二十四節気|1=Solar term|2=ja|3=二十四節気|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Seasonal Month|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Seasonal Month|qq=}} (from {{ill|Jingzhe|lt=Awakening of Insects|ja|啓蟄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jingzhe|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jingzhe|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Qingming|ja|清明|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Qingming|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Qingming|qq=}}) as applicable.

