==Pronunciation== PronounceYin Fire Rabbit
==Years of Yin Fire Rabbit== A year in the [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] that leaves a remainder of 7 when divided by 60 is a [[:en:Year|year]] of {{ill|Teibou|ja|1=Yin Fire Rabbit|qq=ja|丁卯|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teibou|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teibou|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Fire Rabbit|qq=}}. {| class="wikitable" |+'''Yin Fire Rabbit (丁卯)'s years table''' |- ! [[:en:1st millennium|1st Millennium]] !! [[:en:2nd millennium|2nd Millennium]] !! [[:en:3rd millennium|3rd Millennium]] |- | * {{ill|7 AD|ja|7年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/7|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=7 AD|qq=}} * [[:en:AD 67|67 AD]] * [[:en:AD 127|127 AD]] * [[:en:187|187 AD]] * [[:en:247|247 AD]] * [[:en:307|307 AD]] * [[:en:367|367 AD]] * [[:en:427|427 AD]] * [[:en:487|487 AD]] * [[:en:547|547 AD]] * [[:en:607|607 AD]] * [[:en:667|667 AD]] * [[:en:AD 727|727 AD]] * [[:en:AD 787|787 AD]] * [[:en:847|847 AD]] * [[:en:907|907 AD]] * [[:en:967|967 AD]] | * [[:en:1027|1027 AD]] * [[:en:1087|1087 AD]] * [[:en:1147|1147 AD]] * [[:en:1207|1207 AD]] * [[:en:1267|1267 AD]] * [[:en:1327|1327 AD]] * [[:en:1387|1387 AD]] * [[:en:1447|1447 AD]] * [[:en:1507|1507 AD]] * [[:en:1567|1567 AD]] * [[:en:1627|1627 AD]] * [[:en:1687|1687 AD]] * [[:en:1747|1747 AD]] * [[:en:1807|1807 AD]] * [[:en:1867|1867 AD]] * [[:en:1927|1927 AD]] * [[:en:1987|1987 AD]] | * {{ill|2047 AD|ja|2047年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2047|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2047 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2107 AD|ja|2107年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2107|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2107 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2167 AD|ja|2167年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2167|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2167 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2227 AD|ja|2227年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2227|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2227 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2287 AD|ja|2287年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Im