{{infobox Chinese|l=Yin Fire Rabbit|kanji=丁卯|romaji=hinoto usagi|onyomi=tei bō|p=dīngmǎo|w=ting-mao|mi=tʰiŋ⁵³ mɑʊ̯²¹|y=deng1 maau5|j=deng1 maau5|ci=tɛŋ maːu̯²|mc=tæŋ mawX|oc-bs=tæŋ mruʔ|qq=}} {{Otheruseslist|十干十二支の丁卯|日本海軍軍艦もしくはChōshū Domainの丁卯丸|第一丁卯|もう一隻の日本海軍軍艦|第二丁卯|qq=}} {{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}} '''Yin Fire Rabbit also known as 丁卯''' (hinotou, teika nou, teika nousagi, teibou) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.
It is the 4th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}, preceded by {{ill|Bingyin|ja|丙寅|1=Yang Fire Tiger|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bingyin|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bingyin|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Tiger|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Wuchun|ja|戊辰|1=Yang Earth Dragon|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wuchun|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wuchun|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Earth Dragon|qq=}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]] symbol {{ill|Tei|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|lt=Hinoto (丁)|2=ja|3=丁|4=zh|5=丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tei|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoto (丁)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tei|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoto (丁)|qq=}} represents yin {{ill|Fire|ja|Fire (火)|1=Fire (wuxing)|ja|Fire (火)|1=Fire (wuxing)|lt=Fire (火)|2=uk|3=Вогонь (У-сін)|4=bcl|5=Kalayo (wuxing)|6=pt|7=Fogo (astrologia)|8=vi|9=Hỏa (Ngũ hành)|10=ar|11=النار (وو شينغ)|lt=Fire (火)|lt=Fire (火)|2=uk|3=Вогонь (У-сін)|4=bcl|5=Kalayo (wuxing)|6=pt|7=Fogo (astrologia)|8=vi|9=Hỏa (Ngũ hành)|10=ar|11=النار (وو شينغ)|1=Fire (wuxing)|ja|Fire (火)|1=Fire (wuxing)|lt=Fire (火)|2=uk|3=Вогонь (У-сін)|4=bcl|5=Kalayo (wuxing)|6=pt|7=Fogo (astrologia)|8=vi|9=Hỏa (Ngũ hành)|10=ar|11=النار (وو شينغ)|lt=Fire (火)|lt=Fire (火)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fire|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fire|13=User:Immanuelle/Fire (wuxing)|ja|Fire (火)|1=Fire (wuxing)|lt=Fire (火)|2=uk|3=Вогонь (У-сін)|4=bcl|5=Kalayo (wuxing)|6=pt|7=Fogo (astrologia)|8=vi|9=Hỏa (Ngũ hành)|10=ar|11=النار (وو شينغ)|lt=Fire (火)|qq=}}, while the [[:en:Earthly Branches|Earthly Branches]] symbol {{ill|Rabbit|ja|卯|1=Rabbit (Zodiac)|lt=Rabbit (卯)|2=ja|3=卯|1=Rabbit (zodiac)|2=ja|3=卯|4=fr|5=Lapin (astrologie chinoise)|6=nl|7=Konijn (astrologie)|lt=Rabbit (卯)|1=Rabbit (zodiac)|lt=Rabbit (卯)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rabbit|13=User:Immanuelle/Rabbit (zodiac)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rabbit|13=User:Immanuelle/Rabbit (Zodiac)|qq=}} represents yin {{ill|Wood|ja|Wood (木)|1=Wood (wuxing)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|2=uk|3=Дерево (елемент)|4=id|5=Kayu (Wu Xing)|6=ms|7=Kayu (Wu Xing)|8=bcl|9=Kahoy (wuxing)|10=ca|11=Fusta (wuxing)|12=it|13=Legno (elemento)|14=es|15=Madera (Wu Xing)|16=nl|17=Hout (element)|18=vi|19=Mộc (Ngũ hành)|20=tr|21=Tahta (klasik element)|22=ta|23=மரம் (சீன மெய்யியல்)|2=it|3=Legno (elemento)|4=es|5=Madera (Wu Xing)|6=tr|7=Tahta (klasik element)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|lt=Wood (木)|2=uk|3=Дерево (елемент)|4=id|5=Kayu (Wu Xing)|6=ms|7=Kayu (Wu Xing)|8=bcl|9=Kahoy (wuxing)|10=ca|11=Fusta (wuxing)|12=it|13=Legno (elemento)|14=es|15=Madera (Wu Xing)|16=nl|17=Hout (element)|18=vi|19=Mộc (Ngũ hành)|20=tr|21=Tahta (klasik element)|22=ta|23=மரம் (சீன மெய்யியல்)|2=it|3=Legno (elemento)|4=es|5=Madera (Wu Xing)|6=tr|7=Tahta (klasik element)|1=Wood (wuxing)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|2=uk|3=Дерево (елемент)|4=id|5=Kayu (Wu Xing)|6=ms|7=Kayu (Wu Xing)|8=bcl|9=Kahoy (wuxing)|10=ca|11=Fusta (wuxing)|12=it|13=Legno (elemento)|14=es|15=Madera (Wu Xing)|16=nl|17=Hout (element)|18=vi|19=Mộc (Ngũ hành)|20=tr|21=Tahta (klasik element)|22=ta|23=மரம் (சீன மெய்யியல்)|2=it|3=Legno (elemento)|4=es|5=Madera (Wu Xing)|6=tr|7=Tahta (klasik element)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|lt=Wood (木)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wood|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wood|13=User:Immanuelle/Wood (wuxing)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|2=uk|3=Дерево (елемент)|4=id|5=Kayu (Wu Xing)|6=ms|7=Kayu (Wu Xing)|8=bcl|9=Kahoy (wuxing)|10=ca|11=Fusta (wuxing)|12=it|13=Legno (elemento)|14=es|15=Madera (Wu Xing)|16=nl|17=Hout (element)|18=vi|19=Mộc (Ngũ hành)|20=tr|21=Tahta (klasik element)|22=ta|23=மரம் (சீன மெய்யியல்)|2=it|3=Legno (elemento)|4=es|5=Madera (Wu Xing)|6=tr|7=Tahta (klasik element)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|qq=}}, forming a generating relationship ({{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|五行思想#相生（そうじょう）|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Generation|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Generation|qq=}}) (i.e. Wood gives rise to Fire).
==Pronunciation== PronounciationYin Fire Rabbit \n<!-- == * Yin Fire Rabbit (丁卯) ** Chinese (Mandarin Pinyin): dīngmǎo ** Cantonese (Jyutping): ding1 maau2 ** Japanese: ***Kunyomi: ひのとう (hino-tō) ***Onyomi: ていかのうさぎ (teika-no-usagi) ***Onyomi: ていぼう (teibō) ** Korean (Revised Romanization): jeongmyo ** Vietnamese (Hán-Việt): Đinh Mão
--> ==Years of Yin Fire Rabbit== A year in the [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] that leaves a remainder of 7 when divided by 60 is a [[:en:Year|year]] of {{ill|Teibou|ja|1=Yin Fire Rabbit|qq=ja|丁卯|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teibou|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teibou|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Fire Rabbit|qq=}}. {| class="wikitable" |+'''Yin Fire Rabbit (丁卯)'s years table''' |- ! [[:en:1st millennium|1st Millennium]] !! [[:en:2nd millennium|2nd Millennium]] !! [[:en:3rd millennium|3rd Millennium]] |- | * {{ill|7 AD|ja|7年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/7|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=7 AD|qq=}} * [[:en:AD 67|67 AD]] * [[:en:AD 127|127 AD]] * [[:en:187|187 AD]] * [[:en:247|247 AD]] * [[:en:307|307 AD]] * [[:en:367|367 AD]] * [[:en:427|427 AD]] * [[:en:487|487 AD]] * [[:en:547|547 AD]] * [[:en:607|607 AD]] * [[:en:667|667 AD]] * [[:en:AD 727|727 AD]] * [[:en:AD 787|787 AD]] * [[:en:847|847 AD]] * [[:en:907|907 AD]] * [[:en:967|967 AD]] | * [[:en:1027|1027 AD]] * [[:en:1087|1087 AD]] * [[:en:1147|1147 AD]] * [[:en:1207|1207 AD]] * [[:en:1267|1267 AD]] * [[:en:1327|1327 AD]] * [[:en:1387|1387 AD]] * [[:en:1447|1447 AD]] * [[:en:1507|1507 AD]] * [[:en:1567|1567 AD]] * [[:en:1627|1627 AD]] * [[:en:1687|1687 AD]] * [[:en:1747|1747 AD]] * [[:en:1807|1807 AD]] * [[:en:1867|1867 AD]] * [[:en:1927|1927 AD]] * [[:en:1987|1987 AD]] | * {{ill|2047 AD|ja|2047年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2047|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2047 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2107 AD|ja|2107年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2107|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2107 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2167 AD|ja|2167年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2167|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2167 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2227 AD|ja|2227年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2227|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2227 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2287 AD|ja|2287年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2287|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2287 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2347 AD|ja|2347年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2347|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2347 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2407 AD|ja|2407年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2407|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2407 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2467 AD|ja|2467年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2467|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2467 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2527 AD|ja|2527年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2527|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2527 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2587 AD|ja|2587年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2587|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2587 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2647 AD|ja|2647年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2647|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2647 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2707 AD|ja|2707年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2707|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2707 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2767 AD|ja|2767年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2767|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2767 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2827 AD|ja|2827年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2827|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2827 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2887 AD|ja|2887年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2887|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2887 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2947 AD|ja|2947年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2947|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2947 AD|qq=}} |}
==Months of Yin Fire Rabbit== In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 4 or 9 (when the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]] are {{ill|Kou|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|lt=Kinoe (甲)|2=ja|3=甲|4=zh|5=甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=}} or {{ill|Otsu|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|lt=Tsuchinoto (己)|2=ja|3=己|4=zh|5=己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:February|February]] is designated as the [[:en:Month|month (calendar)]] of {{ill|Teibou|ja|1=Yin Fire Rabbit|qq=ja|丁卯|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teibou|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teibou|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Fire Rabbit|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the [[:en:Solar term|Solar term]] (from [[:en:Jingzhe|Awakening of Insects]] until the day before [[:en:Qingming (solar term)|Qingming]]) as applicable.
